item.title: City take Ming Chuan University to school
item.description: by Michael Christie Venue: Ming Chuan University Campus, Tao Yuan Time:Â Sat Sept 5th, 4.30pm Conditions: Dry and hot Here was a game with lots of chances at both ends and generally good performances from both teams. On a dry, uneven pitch, Ming Chuan University arguably started better with their triangular passing causing problems down both flanks early on. It was from this kind of attack that they opened the scoring.
